{"title":"Dolor_Medio_Facial","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología/Dolor_Medio_Facial.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"Dolor Medio\\NFacial","guid":"FMI70fXHS_mGAJZAySsgWA","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Anatomía\\NFuncional","guid":"ypRO-TW7ROmtSyKsHjFYSg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"Territorio del nervio\\Ntrigémino (V par)","guid":"flu8iCKQSbCAAhVQx5dLRg","children":[{"id":"3","parent":"2","text":"V1 Oftálmico → frente, párpado superior, dorso nasal","guid":"0Qfips9qQq6anza7j7ktZg","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"2","text":"V2 Maxilar → PRINCIPAL\\Nen dolor medio facial","guid":"ObezEpCTRMaEyiSA9LFVuQ","children":[{"id":"5","parent":"4","text":"Infraorbitario → mejilla, labio superior, ala nasal","guid":"xrk_u4qmQXKjf0nklmHRxA","children":[]},{"id":"6","parent":"4","text":"Palatinos → paladar duro y blando","guid":"eu_oiX38TnWsDANw-5TEyQ","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"4","text":"Alveolares superiores → dientes maxilares, encía, seno maxilar","guid":"-mjryUggSRShjboWa3VDIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"8","parent":"2","text":"V3 Mandibular → mentón, mandíbula, lengua anterior","guid":"uvvKBzB5Sm-FSCQnkydPDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"9","parent":"1","text":"Inervación autonómica → ganglio esfenopalatino (pterigopalatino)","guid":"mbMTiKBMSZajSVeKtbEZ_w","children":[{"id":"10","parent":"9","text":"Parasimpático → lagrimeo, congestión nasal, rinorrea","guid":"URlp7ZoETh-TzrS0oe1-Ng","children":[]},{"id":"11","parent":"9","text":"Simpático → vasomotor facial","guid":"K1zEbHf7Rayd0vy-fn4qMg","children":[]}]},{"id":"12","parent":"1","text":"Senos paranasales → maxilar, etmoidal, frontal, esfenoidal","guid":"_wOK8CF9SnSQcRL5Bfxo6A","children":[]},{"id":"13","parent":"1","text":"Articulación temporomandibular (ATM)","guid":"hkKgxTcnQ26U98MbvxscRQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"14","parent":"0","text":"Clasificación\\Npor Mecanismo","guid":"Slmjz5C_Q62P7Wrs4-vAtA","children":[{"id":"15","parent":"14","text":"DENTAL Y PERIODONTAL →\\Ncausa MÁS FRECUENTE de\\Ndolor facial agudo","guid":"y2gkQIjvQ26E-od2y1aHRA","children":[{"id":"16","parent":"15","text":"Pulpitis (reversible/irreversible)","guid":"jXik8fxaQEWTVfX0QBHiOw","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"15","text":"Absceso periapical","guid":"PEaEB088RUWXtbcwInR3mw","children":[]},{"id":"18","parent":"15","text":"Periodontitis","guid":"Lple3OV2Q3ShALd6AZ8JmQ","children":[]},{"id":"19","parent":"15","text":"Alveolitis seca post-extracción","guid":"HBMUg8cHQKGmslW9fZBgMQ","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"15","text":"Fractura dental/radicular","guid":"4BJy4JvkQS-yxP43FfXl-A","children":[]}]},{"id":"21","parent":"14","text":"SINUSAL","guid":"ybrva47nQeiHaN2VubhjlQ","children":[{"id":"22","parent":"21","text":"Rinosinusitis aguda bacteriana","guid":"XSax0cB-SEy7Wgkeo8qjew","children":[]},{"id":"23","parent":"21","text":"Rinosinusitis crónica con/sin pólipos","guid":"jk3ez8GwSdOg87m3xBsO9A","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"21","text":"Sinusitis fúngica (invasiva en inmunosuprimidos)","guid":"JbwrCqnfRaqvOnpd-SKBVQ","children":[]},{"id":"25","parent":"21","text":"Barosinusitis","guid":"UPW8yHN1Rzm7xRHEEG3Fqg","children":[]}]},{"id":"26","parent":"14","text":"NEUROVASCULAR\\N(cefaleas primarias)","guid":"-O-yXoYwR4Cz7zt8gl-vbQ","children":[{"id":"27","parent":"26","text":"Migraña con aura facial → V2 territorio","guid":"hC8XA9ZKSxC1OWBQPLUHOA","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"26","text":"Cefaleas trigémino-autonómicas\\N(TACs)","guid":"eT2OCYpYRS6DXd-p-0gs0g","children":[{"id":"29","parent":"28","text":"Cefalea en racimos → orbital/temporal/medio facial","guid":"G9ScOMhsTBqflXBVvnPWuA","children":[]},{"id":"30","parent":"28","text":"Hemicránea paroxística","guid":"vN9LRz0tRtC00tNKkxTIlA","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"28","text":"SUNCT/SUNA","guid":"xhFPbTiDS8qpr9OkT9RYZg","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"26","text":"Cefalea tensional con irradiación facial","guid":"OIFJmTmYRUaLUJwDmjp5RQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"33","parent":"14","text":"NEUROPÁTICO","guid":"oeC6audqS8Cyj5c6wjbPWw","children":[{"id":"34","parent":"33","text":"Neuralgia del trigémino CLÁSICA","guid":"UFhmd6c_Q2KDm2LWcx-JAg","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"33","text":"Neuralgia del trigémino SECUNDARIA (EM, tumor)","guid":"YQsm7hF5Q6KjqYCHvs5WjQ","children":[]},{"id":"36","parent":"33","text":"Neuropatía trigeminal dolorosa post-traumática","guid":"M36IiJZ0TAi-V4TeJVGXbw","children":[]},{"id":"37","parent":"33","text":"Neuralgia post-herpética (V1 > V2)","guid":"kZj8lEy0Q-uDkbP-EDqdJw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"33","text":"Síndrome de boca ardiente","guid":"XT5FogCmSD24SHghr8ZZ-Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"14","text":"MUSCULOESQUELÉTICO","guid":"I6N8cqpERKWifStZC_1TDA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"Trastornos\\Ntemporomandibulares\\N(TTM)","guid":"GYQ_wJh8TQeeqzbp_BneEA","children":[{"id":"41","parent":"40","text":"Mialgia de músculos masticatorios","guid":"YJrvgZswSq6zzkLSg9KRwg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"40","text":"Artralgia ATM","guid":"lfaeMgBbSQq2eUt96nTW_Q","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"40","text":"Desplazamiento discal con/sin reducción","guid":"d36i_HJnQW-q1Y7MCaIsGg","children":[]}]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"Dolor miofascial referido → trigger points masétero, temporal","guid":"smnYd3p7Qx-1fdwBrIGOvA","children":[]}]},{"id":"45","parent":"14","text":"VASCULAR","guid":"eqGW5sKhQ7i0lgsjm1Dypg","children":[{"id":"46","parent":"45","text":"Arteritis de células gigantes → EMERGENCIA en >50 años","guid":"RdamDEb6RxKzFkxLiETa-g","children":[]},{"id":"47","parent":"45","text":"Disección carotídea","guid":"cp6eNG1vS9mwtGsTJvSfYg","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"45","text":"Malformaciones arteriovenosas","guid":"4hHFrbt5SL26SsNZvNw7Bw","children":[]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"14","text":"NEOPLÁSICO","guid":"FP4QgaOQRcGV33L_JjDVgg","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"Carcinoma nasofaríngeo → SOSPECHAR si dolor persistente + síntomas nasales","guid":"T0nn08yiQuihf_oHqCzBww","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"Tumores de senos paranasales","guid":"yCLb7YTLSQ62ITvwSgVYpw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"Schwannoma trigeminal","guid":"itKRLIb4Qbit6KCBoI_5LA","children":[]},{"id":"53","parent":"49","text":"Metástasis base de cráneo","guid":"zjzHbJGkRiWqXy_ze3Q2tQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"54","parent":"14","text":"REFERIDO Y\\NMISCELÁNEO","guid":"aQp0Q1tMT8m58FrhIsxPtQ","children":[{"id":"55","parent":"54","text":"Dolor cardíaco referido a mandíbula → IAM atípico","guid":"xSO9egRJRiSo7XDmBjhTKw","children":[]},{"id":"56","parent":"54","text":"Dolor ocular (glaucoma agudo, uveítis)","guid":"bGhUc8KyQtCHGWs8Mda85Q","children":[]},{"id":"57","parent":"54","text":"Otitis media","guid":"nleqkH7iR7a03u3Ej62Syw","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"54","text":"Sialoadenitis/sialolitiasis","guid":"6DVVMcgOT-O14olc0kzyJQ","children":[]},{"id":"59","parent":"54","text":"Dolor psicógeno (dolor facial persistente idiopático)","guid":"puNvGLLrTWapqZxcoN4hVQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"0","text":"Evaluación\\Nen Urgencias","guid":"G6MvUzf3T3GxWjKftog9IQ","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"Anamnesis\\Ndirigida","guid":"a_SkxgG6TSuJ8O4x2Q-yXQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"Localización PRECISA → unilateral vs bilateral","guid":"pDLfU4oQSr-2HCbppdwdMw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"Temporalidad → agudo vs crónico, episódico vs continuo","guid":"Yz7d3jC5S5SMKU5SIsVjhg","children":[]},{"id":"64","parent":"61","text":"Carácter → lancinante (neuropático), pulsátil (vascular), sordo (sinusal/dental)","guid":"0Fa5WgUtQnm12qXpww1RwQ","children":[]},{"id":"65","parent":"61","text":"Triggers → masticación (TTM/dental), táctil (neuralgia), Valsalva (sinusal)","guid":"s3no0D-tQEyId8LG3taqxg","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"61","text":"Síntomas autonómicos → lagrimeo, rinorrea, congestión (TACs)","guid":"_F45uAgVTmG48cjeXCuxbQ","children":[]},{"id":"67","parent":"61","text":"Red flags → fiebre, pérdida de peso, déficit neurológico, diplopia","guid":"tqcd7ee-RUKOGQZ5RtsoQQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"68","parent":"60","text":"Examen\\Nfísico","guid":"C_LL1N5USou71L4XdW567w","children":[{"id":"69","parent":"68","text":"Inspección facial → asimetría, edema, eritema","guid":"fwDjwxcKQIO--kfM3Vg_yA","children":[]},{"id":"70","parent":"68","text":"Palpación senos → dolor frontal, maxilar, etmoidal","guid":"C0iyJEPfQCekyJ8QNBgwRw","children":[]},{"id":"71","parent":"68","text":"Palpación ATM → click, crepitación, dolor","guid":"SoOj-TdSQxyPs9B-fGqu8g","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"68","text":"Palpación músculos masticatorios → masétero, temporal, pterigoideos","guid":"UOdmX8zdQB-BaOOXhjyi7A","children":[]},{"id":"73","parent":"68","text":"Examen dental → percusión, vitalidad, movilidad","guid":"T6F74hAbSeOlf2Fq9akzsA","children":[]},{"id":"74","parent":"68","text":"Examen neurológico → sensibilidad V1-V2-V3, reflejo corneal","guid":"otW0cv3-Rg-Hp4kW9iWsSA","children":[]},{"id":"75","parent":"68","text":"Otoscopia → descartar otitis referida","guid":"M6xrAuxAQ7-YBjbD7vjDMg","children":[]},{"id":"76","parent":"68","text":"Rinoscopia anterior → pólipos, secreción purulenta","guid":"vdsZf5HXQXarUGw3S531ew","children":[]}]},{"id":"77","parent":"60","text":"Laboratorio","guid":"fOor552bRRK3MC6jlJDIZA","children":[{"id":"78","parent":"77","text":"Hemograma → leucocitosis (infección)","guid":"oUKKTvPaSVGyrzYEkD9deA","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"77","text":"PCR/VHS → VHS >50 mm/h sospechar arteritis temporal en >50a","guid":"1Y2kzjx6TeOtS4vqYslI0A","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"77","text":"Procalcitonina → si sospecha infección severa","guid":"0TODp9QJTYmkcpMA4j6Org","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"60","text":"Imágenes","guid":"3Tc2aKsGS3-bkiBECjNYtg","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"TC senos paranasales → gold standard sinusitis complicada","guid":"X43TB3k3S3Gsst0BaCRutg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"OPG (ortopantomografía) → patología dental/mandibular","guid":"FCEy7aa4SBG_bE96CXdKHw","children":[]},{"id":"84","parent":"81","text":"RM cerebral → sospecha neuropatía, tumor, EM","guid":"Gm69mc8zQDeHhXARhGEkzA","children":[]},{"id":"85","parent":"81","text":"Angio-TC/RM → si sospecha vascular","guid":"WfqvnKudT8mvwl0scDF-Cw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"86","parent":"0","text":"Manejo por\\NEtiología","guid":"BpsNZstrTemOlBvxYkhPgg","children":[{"id":"87","parent":"86","text":"Dental → derivación odontológica\\N+ analgesia","guid":"VwoHBwVBThetsf7Zj6Lc_g","children":[{"id":"88","parent":"87","text":"Ibuprofeno 400-600 mg c/8h + Paracetamol 1g c/8h (combinación sinérgica)","guid":"mVq6nO_JTnOCfgHseXRbMg","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"87","text":"ATB si absceso → Amoxicilina 875/125 mg c/12h o Clindamicina 300 mg c/8h","guid":"2cJPh4DyRHeYL-rg0w7BDw","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"86","text":"Rinosinusitis\\Naguda","guid":"QYC7yzszTluQj1ZE0Dv6RA","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"Mayoría VIRAL → NO requiere ATB","guid":"9iJJFTmtRcSIBCAmPuWv6w","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"ATB solo si >10 días sin mejoría o empeoramiento tras mejoría inicial","guid":"ErxVDswKQkWYnzhoH0LZ7A","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"Amoxicilina/Ác. clavulánico 875/125 mg c/12h x 5-7 días","guid":"P2mx5Dg_R1im6MjvbEDY5w","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"Corticoides intranasales → mometasona, fluticasona","guid":"rcFR86CJTsaR9KnErs1Ikg","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"Lavados nasales con solución salina","guid":"Qj9yLA9zToeEngKRHxl_Ng","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"Descongestionantes tópicos → máximo 3-5 días (rinitis medicamentosa)","guid":"_n4Hw5lZQ4qGDCl_39YieA","children":[]}]},{"id":"97","parent":"86","text":"Neuralgia del\\Ntrigémino","guid":"zQBrc95NRTW4tDlBRulmHQ","children":[{"id":"98","parent":"97","text":"PRIMERA LÍNEA →\\NCarbamazepina 100-200 mg c/12h\\N(titular)","guid":"7eesoVPeRmiOJi6jGvZzuA","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"NNT 1.7-1.8 para alivio significativo","guid":"iD5d3gWqTae0t2fesl1Psg","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"Monitorizar Na+, hemograma, función hepática","guid":"uPXjT2DhS0GS0QCa8e33tA","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"97","text":"Oxcarbazepina 300 mg c/12h → alternativa, menos efectos adversos","guid":"_SqT9X3AT-iuxZinKRvRuQ","children":[]},{"id":"102","parent":"97","text":"Refractarios → derivación neurocirugía (descompresión microvascular, radiocirugía)","guid":"FWqMdJCJRU6ERfUXxEDxbw","children":[]}]},{"id":"103","parent":"86","text":"Cefaleas\\Ntrigémino-autonómicas","guid":"Bc-AWHJBRZmNfRbpbDC0_g","children":[{"id":"104","parent":"103","text":"Cefalea en racimos aguda → O2 al 100% 12-15 L/min x 15 min + Sumatriptán 6 mg SC","guid":"a3Ivd1nxTnKLAzD2uG1Uyw","children":[]},{"id":"105","parent":"103","text":"Preventivo → Verapamilo 240-960 mg/día (monitorizar ECG)","guid":"9zpXfTPxRtqoQEA_wv2XLw","children":[]}]},{"id":"106","parent":"86","text":"Trastornos\\Ntemporomandibulares","guid":"iKKyHQBaTCKdNTnkiCmLyQ","children":[{"id":"107","parent":"106","text":"Educación + automanejo → PRIMERA LÍNEA","guid":"6NKLZw5uTpmUnfmtefdYsQ","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"106","text":"Fisioterapia → ejercicios de rango de movimiento","guid":"o1CasdPQQRWqvYw50Skz2Q","children":[]},{"id":"109","parent":"106","text":"Férula oclusal nocturna","guid":"QwntKTpTQJq0DV8ydrrF5Q","children":[]},{"id":"110","parent":"106","text":"AINEs corto plazo","guid":"ZXs1kiL6R7-acZLdeWbY-A","children":[]},{"id":"111","parent":"106","text":"Amitriptilina 10-25 mg nocturna si crónico","guid":"b76bATU8Q3aPM7xacIN6vg","children":[]}]},{"id":"112","parent":"86","text":"Arteritis de células gigantes\\N→ EMERGENCIA","guid":"-2cQ5Mr8RHOXfeA-Z-9lSQ","children":[{"id":"113","parent":"112","text":"Prednisona 40-60 mg/día INMEDIATO si sospecha clínica","guid":"y3fHi4PcS7atYrhlUJA3EQ","children":[]},{"id":"114","parent":"112","text":"NO esperar biopsia para iniciar tratamiento","guid":"1infJoR_RT-3zizUC5blVQ","children":[]},{"id":"115","parent":"112","text":"Biopsia arteria temporal dentro de 2 semanas","guid":"HiN7lXGdQhuKh3_Xc_AKCA","children":[]},{"id":"116","parent":"112","text":"Riesgo ceguera irreversible si no se trata","guid":"S88mZ1n0TiGi7x92GaS9eg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"117","parent":"0","text":"Consideraciones\\NGeriátricas","guid":"bqhR3koOS9SA0HSI6u1cew","children":[{"id":"118","parent":"117","text":"Presentación\\Natípica frecuente","guid":"n4uiIiSKTuuooesgu73PKw","children":[{"id":"119","parent":"118","text":"Dolor menos localizado","guid":"qqFqaRsfTTKInnuUqBR2Ng","children":[]},{"id":"120","parent":"118","text":"Mayor prevalencia de causas secundarias (neoplasia, arteritis)","guid":"8tPg3Vu1ReiJI5nMVMH-Jw","children":[]},{"id":"121","parent":"118","text":"Neuralgia del trigémino → descartar causa secundaria en >60a (RM obligatoria)","guid":"Iw21T-0tQ3qYv21B0JY29g","children":[]}]},{"id":"122","parent":"117","text":"Arteritis de células\\Ngigantes","guid":"K0VRPeYYTTaMhBflUE416Q","children":[{"id":"123","parent":"122","text":"Incidencia aumenta con edad → peak 70-80 años","guid":"Xxse8jprQtC3MznPH1RLDg","children":[]},{"id":"124","parent":"122","text":"VHS >50 + cefalea nueva + claudicación mandibular → TRATAR INMEDIATO","guid":"ICuALk3mQlu9WzQcga0zGQ","children":[]},{"id":"125","parent":"122","text":"Sensibilidad VHS 76-86%, PCR más sensible","guid":"qbj9qF7ER2OEh7Hv97bT9g","children":[]}]},{"id":"126","parent":"117","text":"Fármacos →\\Najuste obligatorio","guid":"cFp6qsEkTPOGKFT1Ving-w","children":[{"id":"127","parent":"126","text":"Carbamazepina → mayor riesgo hiponatremia en AM, interacciones múltiples","guid":"fKNHo0LcRS-vdka7CyEGfQ","children":[]},{"id":"128","parent":"126","text":"AINEs → precaución ERC, ICC, anticoagulantes","guid":"Pv4HJj_pRtadEGjbIK09-A","children":[]},{"id":"129","parent":"126","text":"Amitriptilina → carga anticolinérgica, retención urinaria, confusión","guid":"k2naoXxPS8yRC3rpMgJU4Q","children":[]},{"id":"130","parent":"126","text":"Opioides → mayor riesgo delirium, constipación","guid":"HgIfu-4fSyGW7KDd_kmd5A","children":[]}]},{"id":"131","parent":"117","text":"Dolor dental\\Nen AM","guid":"8IYWHF2nQi2RVwqDCJEVaw","children":[{"id":"132","parent":"131","text":"Boca seca (xerostomía) por polifarmacia → caries radiculares frecuentes","guid":"vKDcK0QCRzq5cs-WmvggAg","children":[]},{"id":"133","parent":"131","text":"Prótesis mal ajustadas → estomatitis protésica","guid":"XohWyI2zSb2eD1pugubUyQ","children":[]},{"id":"134","parent":"131","text":"Cáncer oral → lesión ulcerada >2 sem que no cicatriza = biopsia","guid":"Th1s6MyKT6qLvBdmg_gVOQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"135","parent":"117","text":"Dolor facial\\Npersistente idiopático","guid":"mUhnwrK8RKimi1MUugyaew","children":[{"id":"136","parent":"135","text":"Más frecuente en mujeres >40 años","guid":"CF2zYKOmQVyZjShSFNoCvQ","children":[]},{"id":"137","parent":"135","text":"Diagnóstico de exclusión → descartar TODO antes","guid":"pfycB26tQOSZrShFzMrp-Q","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"135","text":"Manejo multidisciplinario → antidepresivos, TCC","guid":"pUNcjb0BT62OyTVzB2dfnQ","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"139","parent":"0","text":"Perlas\\NClínicas","guid":"yv8AHnkRQYir4X09lR_jPA","children":[{"id":"140","parent":"139","text":"Dolor dental es la causa MÁS FRECUENTE de dolor facial agudo","guid":"I9M1oWaXT5G2lpEWndKv4Q","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"139","text":"VHS >50 + cefalea nueva en >50a = arteritis temporal hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"GsZqaVFjTdilL0Y0r2JpGw","children":[]},{"id":"142","parent":"139","text":"Neuralgia del trigémino en <40a → SIEMPRE descartar EM (RM con gadolinio)","guid":"_MF6ikvvTrOsVa9IaFhIqA","children":[]},{"id":"143","parent":"139","text":"Dolor facial + déficit neurológico progresivo = NEOPLASIA hasta demostrar lo contrario","guid":"izDzgT3lRwGdFdED0BHyKg","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"139","text":"Síntomas autonómicos ipsilaterales → pensar en cefaleas trigémino-autonómicas","guid":"afLPE8ciThCFizBGbLSUKQ","children":[]},{"id":"145","parent":"139","text":"Carbamazepina NNT 1.7 para neuralgia trigeminal → fármaco más efectivo en dolor neuropático","guid":"eXrVelYgQ5Cvq800SIGcnw","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"139","text":"Dolor mandibular bilateral + disnea en AM → considerar IAM atípico","guid":"qomIDh4tRdGTF-E79MXsJA","children":[]},{"id":"147","parent":"139","text":"Rinosinusitis aguda es VIRAL en >90% → NO prescribir ATB de rutina","guid":"9R2COimrSWOakIY_uEwdrw","children":[]},{"id":"148","parent":"139","text":"TTM → automanejo y educación son primera línea, NO férula sola","guid":"NInAnupCQ1y-2g0gKQl_RA","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"139","text":"Sinusitis fúngica invasiva → sospechar en inmunosuprimidos con dolor facial + fiebre refractaria","guid":"k3ZQRjHgRfiEKCybi6qxhg","children":[]}]},{"id":"150","parent":"0","text":"Referencias","guid":"8pg7JqaLQ8q3ig6Xu7Wm8A","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"1. Zakrzewska JM. Differential diagnosis of facial pain and guidelines for management. Br J Anaesth. 2013;111(1):95-104.","guid":"ow0xtphkTv2lU_dDHHYECw","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"2. International Headache Society. ICHD-3. Cephalalgia. 2018;38(1):1-211.","guid":"2CaEfNe4TwOajaS-IZNWHg","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"3. Balasubramaniam R, Klasser GD. Trigeminal autonomic cephalalgias. Oral Surg Oral Med. 2007;104(3):345-58.","guid":"8Ft9fCtGSFGpbgQENcKifw","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"150","text":"4. Eigenbrodt AK, et al. Diagnosis and management of migraine in ten steps. Nat Rev Neurol. 2021;17(8):501-514.","guid":"a41NjFqdQne1QLEPCOqJvg","children":[]},{"id":"155","parent":"150","text":"5. Rosenfeld RM, et al. Clinical Practice Guideline: Adult Sinusitis. Otolaryngol Head Neck Surg. 2015;152(2 Suppl):S1-S39.","guid":"nc4Kktk6TLS3QEArz5TxKA","children":[]},{"id":"156","parent":"150","text":"6. Cruccu G, et al. AAN-EFNS guidelines on trigeminal neuralgia management. Eur J Neurol. 2008;15(10):1013-28.","guid":"IidfsT4kQnGNjWilAQeJwg","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":156,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"ORL","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Otorrinolaringología","filename":"Dolor_Medio_Facial","id":"map_1560","resolved_references":[]}